{"title":"RetroArch上手教程","date":"2020-02-07T12:27:34.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 7, 2020","L":"02/07/2020","MM-DD":"02-07"},"thumbnail":"/posts/RetroArch上手教程/retroarch.png","link":"posts/RetroArch上手教程","comments":true,"tags":["模拟器"],"categories":["模拟器"],"updated":"2020-04-22T12:04:40.660Z","content":"<h2 id=\"简介\">简介<a title=\"#简介\" href=\"#简介\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>RetroArch可以在Windows，Mac OS X和Linux等常用平台上运行，但它可以单独支持它，因此可以支持更多平台。</p>\n<p>我们支持甚至Microsoft和Apple本身都不支持的操作系统，例如PowerPC Mac上的macOS X，以及早于Windows 95的Windows OS上都可以使用RetroArch。</p>\n<p>最重要的是，RetroArch还可以在适用于平板电脑和手机的iOS和Android以及PS2，PS3，PSP，PS Vita，Wii，Wii U，2DS，3DS，Switch等游戏机上运行！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"截图\">截图<a title=\"#截图\" href=\"#截图\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/RetroArch%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/WX20200208-122941@2x.png\" alt=\"WX20200208-122941@2x.png\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/RetroArch%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/WX20200208-123006@2x.png\" alt=\"WX20200208-123006@2x.png\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/RetroArch%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/WX20200208-123514@2x.png\" alt=\"WX20200208-123514@2x.png\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/posts/RetroArch%E4%B8%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/WX20200208-123623@2x.png\" alt=\"WX20200208-123623@2x.png\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"下载\">下载<a title=\"#下载\" href=\"#下载\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"模拟器下载\">模拟器下载<a title=\"#模拟器下载\" href=\"#模拟器下载\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"note danger\">\n            <p><strong>RetroArch</strong></p><p><strong>下载地址:</strong>  <a href=\"https://retroarch.com/?page=platforms\" target=\"_blank\">(https://retroarch.com/?page=platforms)</a></p><p>当前的稳定版本是：1.8.4</p><div class=\"text-center\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://buildbot.libretro.com/stable/1.8.4/windows/x86_64/RetroArch-x64-setup.exe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"fa fa-exe\"></i>Windows</a> <a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://buildbot.libretro.com/stable/1.8.4/apple/osx/x86_64/RetroArch.dmg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><i class=\"fa fa-dmg\"></i>MacOS</a></div>\n          </div>\n<h3 id=\"游戏下载地址\">游戏下载地址<a title=\"#游戏下载地址\" href=\"#游戏下载地址\"></a></h3>\n<p><strong>百度云：</strong>(<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WCy6pePZgu86YbCaLPuwmw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1WCy6pePZgu86YbCaLPuwmw</a>)</p>\n<p>包含以下游戏：</p>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th>–英文–</th>\n<th>–中文–</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>SFC ROM（中文）</td>\n<td>FC ROM（英文）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>PEC ROM （中文）</td>\n<td>MAME （英文）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>CPS1 ，CPS2，CPS3 ROM（中文）</td>\n<td>NeoGeo （英文）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>GBA ROM（中文）</td>\n<td>MD ROM（英文）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h2 id=\"模拟器配置\">模拟器配置<a title=\"#模拟器配置\" href=\"#模拟器配置\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"中文设置\">中文设置<a title=\"#中文设置\" href=\"#中文设置\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>由于本软件未对中文配置优化，语言选择“中文”或“繁体中文”时会出现<span class=\"label warn\">???</span>的情况需要自己下载中文字体，菜单样式一般为xmb，样式皮肤一般为monochrome。可以手动修改替换为自己喜欢的样式和皮肤。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"note success\">\n            <p><strong>设置中文方法</strong></p><ol><li>将下载来的&quot;微软雅黑&quot;字体拷出来并改名为<span class=\"label primary\">font.ttf</span>，拷到内存卡<span class=\"label success\">:\\RetroArch\\assets\\xmb\\monochrome&lt;/span&gt;目录下替换</li><li>主菜单 <span class=\"label success\">Settings --&gt; Onscreen Display --&gt; Onscreen Notifications --&gt; Notification Font</span></li><li><span class=\"label success\">User Interface --&gt; Appearance --&gt; Menu Font</span>，选择刚才拷的font.ttf</li><li>主菜单 <span class=\"label success\">Settings --&gt; User --&gt; Language</span> 选择简体中文</li></ol>\n          </div>\n<div class=\"note success\">\n            <p><strong>XMB界面启动方法</strong><br>设置里面-菜单驱动-选<span class=\"label success\">xmb</span>，可以通过修改<span class=\"label success\">User Interface --&gt; Appearance --&gt; Menu Icon Theme</span>切换皮肤主题</p>\n          </div>\n<h3 id=\"核心设置\">核心设置<a title=\"#核心设置\" href=\"#核心设置\"></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>由于刚刚下载的模拟器本体是不带核心的，需要自己下载核心才能加载和模拟对应的游戏</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"note success\">\n            <p><strong>核心安装</strong></p><p>核心安装方法目前有两种：</p><ol><li><p>外部下载导入：</p><p><strong>Windows:</strong> (<a href=\"http://buildbot.libretro.com/nightly/windows/x86_64/latest/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://buildbot.libretro.com/nightly/windows/x86_64/latest/</a>)</p><p><strong>MacOS:</strong> (<a href=\"http://buildbot.libretro.com/nightly/apple/osx/x86/latest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://buildbot.libretro.com/nightly/apple/osx/x86/latest</a>)</p><p>下载好对应的核心之后导入<span class=\"label default\">cores</span>文件夹中</p></li><li><p>内部下载安装：</p><p>可以通过设置路径<span class=\"label success\">Main Menu -&gt; Load Core -&gt;Download a Core</span>来下载想要的核心。</p></li></ol>\n          </div>\n<h3 id=\"游戏扫描\">游戏扫描<a title=\"#游戏扫描\" href=\"#游戏扫描\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"note success\">\n            <p><strong>导入游戏文件夹</strong></p><p>通过设置<span class=\"label success\">Import content -&gt; Scan Directory</span>来设置你要扫描的游戏路径，能够通过核心识别出来的游戏会被自动加入播放列表中，或者通过<span class=\"label success\">Import content -&gt; Manual Scan</span>来主动定制识别规则，扫描成功后生成playlists和database名称</p>\n          </div>\n<h3 id=\"游戏封面\">游戏封面<a title=\"#游戏封面\" href=\"#游戏封面\"></a></h3>\n<div class=\"note success\">\n            <p><strong>游戏截图配置</strong></p><p>首先进入菜单设置，将缩略图选项设置成截屏，找到<span class=\"label success\">Settings -&gt; Directory -&gt; Thumbnails</span>文件夹的路径，将与<span class=\"label danger\">Rom</span>同名的略缩图文件夹导入其中，例如：<span class=\"label success\">RetroArch\\thumbnails\\Sega - Dreamcast\\Named_Snaps</span>，其中Sega - Dreamcast为database名称一般也为核心名称，其中略缩图文件名和游戏文件名相同且后缀格式为<span class=\"label primary\">.png</span>格式，根文件夹名称和database名称一致即可。</p>\n          </div>\n","prev":{"title":"Hexo + inside 博客个性化定制","link":"posts/Hexo-inside个性化定制"},"next":{"title":"巫师三干货收藏","link":"posts/巫师三干货收藏"},"plink":"https://shuntan.github.io/posts/RetroArch上手教程/","toc":[{"id":"简介","title":"简介","index":"1"},{"id":"截图","title":"截图","index":"2"},{"id":"下载","title":"下载","index":"3","children":[{"id":"模拟器下载","title":"模拟器下载","index":"3.1"},{"id":"游戏下载地址","title":"游戏下载地址","index":"3.2"}]},{"id":"模拟器配置","title":"模拟器配置","index":"4","children":[{"id":"中文设置","title":"中文设置","index":"4.1"},{"id":"核心设置","title":"核心设置","index":"4.2"},{"id":"游戏扫描","title":"游戏扫描","index":"4.3"},{"id":"游戏封面","title":"游戏封面","index":"4.4"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Shawntan","link":"<a href=\"https://shuntan.github.io/posts/RetroArch上手教程/\" title=\"RetroArch上手教程\">https://shuntan.github.io/posts/RetroArch上手教程/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow noopener\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"February 7, 2020","updated":"April 22, 2020"}}